casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Douglas Carrol RHOADS.
No. D-2927.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 11, 2016.
Douglas Carrol Rhoads, of Phoenix, Arizona, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
